snippet.title: Sniper Elite 4 - "Karl Fairburne" Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy at Amazon (UK) - PS4/Xbox One: https://amzn.to/2ICjGa4 
Buy at Amazon (USA) – PS4: https://amzn.to/39HDMvr

Deadly accuracy. Tenacity. Ruthlessness - All the attributes that Karl Fairburne will need to face his toughest mission yet - Italy.

Learn more about Sniper Elite 4's unerring hero, Karl Fairburne, in the latest trailer from our 'Intel' series.

Launching 14 Feb 2017.
